overview.en: "MORE.ONE" is a premium airdrop (candy) distribution platform developed by EOS Genesis block producer MEET.ONE, MORE is the token of MORE.ONE: Users can obtain EOS ecology project airdrops (candy) without holding EOS; DAPPs development team (based on EOS) can have a friendly platform to present their ideas to the community and obtain a high quality initial user base; Active promoters of the EOS community will gain more premium airdrops (candy) and benefits based on their contribution.
